<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.4.1">
<l>taṉmukat tuccuṭṭi tūṅkat tūṅkat tavaḻntupōy</l>
<l>poṉmukak kiṇkiṇi yārppap puḻuti yaḷaikiṉṟā</l>
<l>ṉeṉmakaṉ kōvintaṉ kūtti ṉaiyiḷa māmatī</l>
<l>niṉmukam kaṇṇuḷa vākil nīyiṅkē nōkkippō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Great young Moon, if there are eyes in your head,</l>
<l>come here and behold the dancing of my son Govinda</l>
<l>who is covered in dust while the golden anklets tinkle</l>
<l>and, crawling along, the forehead ornament on his face sways to and fro.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
